hopobject.body: Do you play any instruments? cheapest cycle assistance The bigger question mark of the episode is whether a young cheerleader named Kylie will be able to perform in a big competition scheduled in Chicago after busting her knee just days beforehand. Her doctor warns her against, but Kylie's dedication to the team overrules that very sound advice. It's a nice moment in terms of team spirit, but one that also calls into question the motives and judgment of Alisha and Kylie's mother. Still, the team rallies behind their hurt teammate and go on to (easily foreshadowed) glory by winning first place in their division.
